Package: connectedness
Type: Package
Title: Connectedness Metrics for Genetic Evaluation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Alan", "", email = "alan@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Computes connectedness metrics between management units (MUs)
    in animal breeding data, including Coefficient of Determination (CD) and
    Prediction Error Variance of Differences (PEVD), based on the contrast
    approach via Mixed Model Equations (MME). Supports both pedigree-based
    (A-inverse) and user-supplied relationship matrices (e.g. genomic G-inverse).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
